"Fullscreen” icon either on a thumbnail or on the preview."
msgstr ""

#: ../../setup_application/views_settings.rst:129
msgid "The digiKam Full-Screen Configuration Page"
msgstr "La pàgina de configuració de pantalla completa en el digiKam"

#: ../../setup_application/views_settings.rst:131
msgid ""
"If first option is activated the only way to leave the Full Screen Mode is "
"the context menu, the keyboard shortcut :kbd:`Ctrl-Shift-F`. You can work on "
"the images also by choosing functions from the context menu of an icon or "
"the preview."
msgstr ""

